<h3>Conclusion</h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li>The LGTBQ community&nbsp;<strong>needs an anti-discrimination law that empowers them to build productive lives and relationships</strong>&nbsp;irrespective of gender identity or sexual orientation and place the onus to change on state and society and not the individual.</li></ul>
